{"tid":891952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仆街鳥】中國平安成為匯豐控股第一大股東，持股比例為7.01%，或派員進入董事局","createTime":"2018-11-06T13:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T13:03:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a010c0211866c9ccba8adf250c0db96801af9abf","tid":891952,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/images.marketing-interactive.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Nov-14-Anthony-HSBC-lion-HSBC-700x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fimages.marketing-interactive.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FNov-14-Anthony-HSBC-lion-HSBC-700x420.jpg&h=9c29aa76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國平安繼續增持匯豐控股，並一舉成為後者的第一大股東。<br />\n<br />\n　　11月6日，香港交易所網站披露易顯示，中國平安（601318.SH，<a href=\"http://2318.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2318.HK&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a3367dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2318.HK</a>）旗下的平安資產管理有限公司（下稱平安資管）已超越貝萊德集團（BlackRock，Inc．）成為匯豐控股（<a href=\"http://0005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0005.HK&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=760cb7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0005.HK</a>）最大股東，持有約14.19億股股份，持股比例7.01%。以匯豐控股昨日收盤價65.5港元/股計算，這批股份市值約929.4億港元。<br />\n<br />\n中國平安方面向澎湃新聞表示，該投資屬於保險資金的財務性投資，中國平安看好匯豐的發展前景，且匯豐分紅率較高，符合保險資金的風險偏好和投資收益要求。<br />\n<br />\n　　2017年12月，平安資管通過港股通渠道累計買入匯豐控股約合10.18億股，持股比例達到5.01%，超越JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co．成為匯豐控股第二大股東，成為匯豐控股的重要投資者之一。而在16年前，匯豐控股曾是中國平安的股東之一。<br />\n<br />\n　　早在2002年，匯豐控股斥資6億美元認購了中國平安10%的股份。在2007年中國平安上市時，匯豐控股通過其全資子公司&mdash;&mdash;匯豐保險和匯豐銀行合計持有中國平安約合12.33億股，佔當時中國平安發行前總股本的19.9%，位列第一大股東。2012年，匯豐控股將其持有的所有中國平安股份轉讓給正大集團，交易總價約合727.36億港元。自此，匯豐控股退出中國平安股東之列。<br />\n<br />\n　　截至目前，中國平安（<a href=\"http://2318.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2318.HK&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a3367dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2318.HK</a>）的市值為1.4萬億港元，已然超過匯豐控股的1.3萬億港元。"},{"pid":"7ef367f950e5afaabde794ff55a99234fdae6c58","tid":891952,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd3aff4ea607b714d7bc8dabb0c859bb7ef0473","tid":891952,"uid":190540,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae0e04e1aebfe9c02d200a8564556f495ad5fba9","tid":891952,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fbcdc95038bc71b66017d19c148f6052ca57715","tid":891952,"uid":54373,"like":71,"dislike":6,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"得7% 寫到匯豐係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f3f96cb0524cb38519737499f1294fc373bb50","tid":891952,"uid":76216,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7fbcdc95038bc71b66017d19c148f6052ca57715","tid":891952,"uid":54373,"like":71,"dislike":6,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"得7% 寫到匯豐係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"最大真係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d7a7c4511d29bdc8418b534d34b1b9160159a0","tid":891952,"uid":43042,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"以後邊個用匯豐就係5毛<br />\n要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de243cbe4e68212145655d6eaa32f40325817ff","tid":891952,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426939-20181106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426939-20181106.htm&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ea4dfc08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426939-20181106.htm&h=92292e4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426939-20181106.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1426939_1_L_20181106184820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1426939_1_L_20181106184820.jpg&h=04391997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平保取代貝萊德，成為滙控第一大股東。聯交所資料顯示，平保旗下的平安資產管理，上星期四以每股平均價約65.11元，再度增持滙控逾537萬股，持股比例增至7.01%，而貝萊德持股6.59%。<br />\n<br />\n以今日收市價66.05元計，平保持有約14.19億股滙控股份，市值約937億元。<br />\n<br />\n平保自2016年第2季開始透過滬港通買入滙控股份，去年12月持股比例逾5%，今年2月及上星期兩度增持。滙控形容平保是長線投資者，雙方長期維持良好合作關係。內地媒體引述平保指，對滙控的投資屬於保險資金財務性投資，派息率較高，符合保險資金風險偏好及投資收益要求。<br />\n<br />\n滙控單一大股東變成中資機構，市場關注政治因素。"},{"pid":"2f8e1ba790ab50cfa6cda077e1a02dd9500e1901","tid":891952,"uid":79563,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"f1f3f96cb0524cb38519737499f1294fc373bb50","tid":891952,"uid":76216,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7fbcdc95038bc71b66017d19c148f6052ca57715","tid":891952,"uid":54373,"like":71,"dislike":6,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"得7% 寫到匯豐係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"最大真係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"有權入董事局<br />\n同匯控股權分散<br />\n7%可以控制好多野"},{"pid":"028a38395341a481db3478d9f2