br />\n貝萊德係\t6.03%<br />\n假設其餘股權係分散係散戶<br />\n <br />\n咁係開股東大會, 表決議案時, <br />\n真係去英國出席投票 / proxy票既香港散戶係好少, 假設係不足0.5%<br />\n而中國平安只需要派一個代表去投, 就已經好有把握通過到大部份議案<br />\n<br />\n英國既股東會中, 中國平安7.01%, 貝萊德6.03%, 到場散戶0.5%<br />\n貝萊德 + 散戶都只係6.53%, 中國平安一定多過你<br />\n佢個股東大會係英國, 有無咁多散戶咁神心, 飛去英國否決佢? <br />\n除非集體係香港搞 proxy, 個組織度一定唔及中國平安<br />\n大部份散戶不如禁個制沽撚左佢算q數, 唔會去搞"},{"pid":"37d13d0492fd59fe279942f687f3c44b28901889","tid":891952,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"908a711acf021d3f189f6ba0e4fa9a695b1ba655","tid":891952,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7fbcdc95038bc71b66017d19c148f6052ca57715","tid":891952,"uid":54373,"like":71,"dislike":6,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"得7% 寫到匯豐係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"之前海航都做過德意志銀行最大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"海航仆街會被迫賣<br />\n中國平安好唔同"},{"pid":"ba706c4ce3797aff7c84e36a7fa312bad13610ac","tid":891952,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"2318聽日gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b528ec47355c23229646ce96a9545e00314ca3","tid":891952,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"九龍新界都冇得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a63c85eed28094c91aedd0b8d8e125e777dc56","tid":891952,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d1449a547951d4633131e0c13f5a4c1a9d8b4a","tid":891952,"uid":31186,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"cit